WEBVTT

00:01.300 --> 00:02.550
《越狱》 前情提要
Previously on prison break.

00:02.560 --> 00:03.960
你准备什么时候告诉我
When were you planning on

00:03.970 --> 00:06.720
你母亲是幕后主使
Telling me that your mother was behind you on this?

00:06.730 --> 00:09.200
你只有今天一天的时间了
You have today, one day.

00:10.270 --> 00:12.180
当布鲁斯把锡拉带回来的时候
When Burrows brings Scylla back to us,

00:12.190 --> 00:15.730
你就是让他脑袋开花的那个人
You will be the one to put a bullet in his brain.

00:15.740 --> 00:17.740
纳文·班纳吉
Naveen banerjee,

00:17.750 --> 00:20.520
是南都·班纳吉总理的儿子
The son of prime minister Nandu Banerjee.

00:20.530 --> 00:23.640
当这一切都过去了
Soon, this will all be behind us,

00:23.650 --> 00:25.490
我可能还有机会见到我的孙子
And maybe I can meet my grandson.

00:25.500 --> 00:26.610
林肯在哪里
Where's Linc?!

00:26.620 --> 00:28.410
现在正在开一个能源会议
There's an energy conference.

00:28.420 --> 00:30.480
在熊猫湾酒店  他会在那里
The Panda Bay Hotel. He'll be there.

00:30.490 --> 00:31.850
克里斯蒂娜的计划
Christina's plan...

00:31.850 --> 00:33.580
她利用锡拉从中渔利所欠的东风
what she needed to profit from Scylla,

00:33.580 --> 00:36.600
就是一种让事态升级为世界大战的催化剂
an incident that'll domino into global warfare.

00:37.430 --> 00:39.070
不要
No!

00:42.470 --> 00:43.800
他们用林肯的名字租了这个
They rented this in Linc's name.

00:43.810 --> 00:45.380
看看这里  这是个陷阱
Look at this. It's a setup!

00:45.390 --> 00:47.570
弹壳上都是他的指纹
His hands are all over the shells.

00:48.980 --> 00:50.640
林肯这回可是竹篮打水一场空了
Lincoln's right back where he started.

00:50.650 --> 00:52.500
这样对迈克尔太残忍了
It really is too bad about Michael.

00:52.510 --> 00:54.280
我们得赶快离开
We gotta go.

00:58.790 --> 01:00.250
我需要医生
I need a doctor here!

01:07.030 --> 01:09.190
他们在那里
There they are!

01:09.200 --> 01:11.210
他们在楼上
They're up there! They're up there!

01:11.220 --> 01:12.570
我们快上楼
Let's go upstairs, now!

01:12.580 --> 01:14.220
快上  上
Move it, move it!

01:15.840 --> 01:18.330
我们混到人群里面吧
Look, let's just blend into the crowd.

01:18.340 --> 01:19.660
我们不能那么出去
No, we can't go that way.

01:19.670 --> 01:21.420
门锁上了  迈克尔
The door is locked, Michael.

01:21.430 --> 01:23.780
退后
Stand back.

02:03.640 --> 02:05.740
这事越来越麻烦了
This whole thing is falling apart.

02:06.300 --> 02:07.430
你觉得呢
Is it?

02:07.440 --> 02:09.380
真的吗
Is it really?

02:09.390 --> 02:10.550
你觉得现在这样很好笑吗
What, do you think this is funny? Huh?

02:10.560 --> 02:11.720
你觉得这事情会多快
How long do you think it's gonna take

02:11.730 --> 02:13.050
传到将军那里去的
Before the general sees this on the news?

02:13.060 --> 02:14.520
如果他觉得我们拿不到锡拉
If he thinks we can't get Scylla,

02:14.530 --> 02:16.940
你觉得他会花多久时间来灭了我们
How long do you think it's gonna take before he comes after us?

02:16.950 --> 02:18.420
我们的家人也将在劫难逃
And then he comes after our families?

02:18.430 --> 02:20.250
确实很搞笑  对吧
Yeah, it's really funny, isn't it?

02:45.810 --> 02:47.390
迈克尔  你在哪
Michael, where are you?

02:47.400 --> 02:48.390
我们还在宾馆里
We're still in the hotel.

02:48.400 --> 02:49.390
有没有其他办法
Is there any other way

02:49.400 --> 02:50.640
出来的时候不被人发现吗
To get out of here without being seen?

02:50.650 --> 02:52.720
没有  到处都是警察和联邦探员
No, there's cops and feds all over the place.

02:52.730 --> 02:53.810
你拿到锡拉了吗
Did you get Scylla?

02:53.820 --> 02:55.010
没有
No.

02:55.020 --> 02:56.460
有人被暗杀了
Some guy got assassinated.

02:56.470 --> 02:58.410
你猜猜谁又被陷害了
And guess who got set up for it.

02:59.410 --> 03:01.470
我们需要锡拉
We need Scylla.

03:01.480 --> 03:02.820
锡拉不见了
Scylla is gone!

03:02.830 --> 03:04.320
我现在只想
The only thing I care about right now

03:04.330 --> 03:05.470
从这里逃出去
Is getting out of here.

03:05.480 --> 03:06.970
是吗  你能往哪儿逃呢  迈克尔
Oh, yeah? Where you gonna go, Michael, huh?

03:06.980 --> 03:09.750
我们会再次陷入公司的穷追猛打中
With the company breathing down our back again.

03:12.000 --> 03:13.360
斯科菲尔德  我是当
Scofield, it's Don.

03:13.370 --> 03:14.450
你想干什么
What do you want?

03:14.460 --> 03:15.500
帮你解决问题
To try to fix this.

03:15.510 --> 03:16.610
怎么解决
How?

03:16.620 --> 03:17.780
又想背后捅我们一刀
By stabbing us in the back again?

03:17.790 --> 03:19.170
让阿历克斯和我说话
Put alex on.

03:19.180 --> 03:20.950
他现在不太好分心
He's a little preoccupied right now.

03:20.960 --> 03:22.990
如果你想冲我发火
Look, you want to be mad at me,

03:23.000 --> 03:24.890
等我们拿到了锡拉再发火也不迟
be mad at me after we get Scylla back.

03:24.890 --> 03:25.820
现在听我说
Now listen to me.

03:25.820 --> 03:28.380
西南边的卸货区有一扇工业门
Okay, the southwest loading dock is a large industrial door.

03:28.390 --> 03:30.260
不是一个快速逃生口
It's not conducive to a quick exit.

03:30.270 --> 03:32.350
只有一个警察把守着
They only have one cop on it.

03:32.360 --> 03:34.630
你们到门口时  我来解决那个警察
When you get to the door, I can incapacitate the cop.

03:34.640 --> 03:36.720
问题是  我们在宾馆的另一边
Problem is, we're on the other side of the hotel,

03:36.730 --> 03:37.840
而他们把一楼封锁了
and they've got the ground floor covered.

03:37.850 --> 03:39.800
你们在外边还看见了什么
What else can you see on the outside?

03:39.810 --> 03:41.110
没了  只有警察
Nothing, just the cop,

03:41.120 --> 03:44.030
垃圾箱  叉车和装换洗衣服的箱子
A couple of dumpsters, jack pallets and some laundry bins.

03:44.040 --> 03:47.280
那就是说宾馆的洗衣房在另一边
That must mean the on-site laundry's on the other side of the hotel,

03:47.290 --> 03:49.030
靠近卸货区大门
Near the loading dock door.

03:49.040 --> 03:51.520
如果我们能到洗衣房  我们就能到大门
If we get to the laundry, we can get to the door.

03:51.530 --> 03:53.150
你说过我们不能到宾馆另一边
You said we can't make it across the hotel.

03:53.160 --> 03:55.460
但是我们可以从屋顶过去
But we can get access to the roof.

03:56.530 --> 03:58.290
宾馆都是用屋顶通风设备
Hotels use rooftop ventilation,

03:58.300 --> 04:00.130
这样  客人才不会闻到洗衣房的味道
So the hotel guests don't smell the laundry fumes.

04:03.700 --> 04:05.130
那好  那就从通风设施那边
Okay, so, listen, take the ventilation system

04:05.140 --> 04:07.200
到洗衣房  如果你们能到洗衣房
To the laundry room. If you can get to the laundry room,

04:07.210 --> 04:08.890
你们就能到大门口
You're gonna get right by the door.

04:10.380 --> 04:11.840
打开免提功能
Put me on speaker.

04:12.550 --> 04:15.310
阿历克斯  你想摆脱公司对我们的纠缠吗
Alex, you want to get the company off our backs?

04:15.320 --> 04:16.870
到邓恩街4号
Go to 4 Dunn place.

04:16.880 --> 04:18.810
莎拉正看着我妈
Sara's holding my mother there.

04:18.820 --> 04:20.900
让她告诉我们锡拉在什么地方
Make her tell us where Scylla is.

04:20.910 --> 04:22.690
还我们一个清白
And clear our names in all this.

04:24.660 --> 04:28.550
马宏  你一定要想尽一切办法撬开她的嘴
Mahone, you need to do whatever you gotta do to get her talk

04:28.560 --> 04:29.890
你明白吗
You hear me?

04:29.900 --> 04:30.890
该怎么做  就怎么做
Do whatever you gotta do.

04:30.900 --> 04:32.750
明白
Got it.

04:34.540 --> 04:35.650
我们走
Come on.

