暗杀者正是林肯·布鲁斯
Identifying the assailants as none other than Lincoln Burrows,

05:18.350 --> 05:20.710
杀害泰伦斯·斯坦曼的那个嫌疑犯
the man who'd been suspected of murdering Terrence Steadman,

05:20.720 --> 05:22.580
还有他弟弟兼策划者迈克尔·斯科菲尔德
And Michael Scofield, his mastermind brother...

05:22.580 --> 05:24.720
克里斯蒂娜把我们都给耍了
Christina sandbagged all of us!

05:26.800 --> 05:28.630
如果他们兄弟俩被抓了
If the brothers are caught,

05:28.640 --> 05:30.210
我们就不能保证
We have no control over what

05:30.220 --> 05:31.970
他们会对警察说什么了
They might say to the authorities.

05:31.980 --> 05:33.470
到酒店去
Get down to that hotel

05:33.480 --> 05:35.790
保证他们不会胡说八道
And make sure they don't have that opportunity.

05:35.800 --> 05:39.290
将军  我非常愿意来接手这项行动
Uh, general, I'd be more than willing to take on that assignment.

05:39.300 --> 05:41.590
我保证  我一定会指挥有方的
And I assure you I will dispatch of it efficiently.

05:41.600 --> 05:44.430
泰迪  我们不是在玩捕猎游戏
This is not an alabama coon hunt, Teddy.

05:44.440 --> 05:46.960
别以为我是一时冲动
Don't judge me by desperate actions

05:46.970 --> 05:48.600
刀架在脖子上的日子我都挺过来了
I've taken when there's been a gun to my head.

05:48.610 --> 05:50.320
我领导监狱里的黑帮
I ran an entire prison gang syndicate.

05:50.330 --> 05:51.820
再心狠手辣的罪犯都奉我为上宾
Hardened felons called me "Mister."

05:51.830 --> 05:54.110
我不是一个告密的小人
I'm so much more than a snitch.

05:54.120 --> 05:55.970
如果你以为我只是那样的人
And if you continue to treat me as such,

05:55.980 --> 05:59.140
那就是你的损失  我无所谓  将军阁下
It will be your loss, General, not mine.

05:59.150 --> 06:02.950
孩子  我手里掌握着一家几百万亿
Son, I have the fate of a multi-trillion dollar

06:02.950 --> 06:04.620
资产公司的命运
enterprise in my hands,

06:04.630 --> 06:10.960
你认为现在我会让你大出风头吗
And you want me to let you earn your stripes now?!

06:11.850 --> 06:13.570
摆平那兄弟俩
Take care of the brothers.

06:24.510 --> 06:27.150
应该是这了
This should be it.

06:30.990 --> 06:32.450
好极了
Perfect.

06:35.290 --> 06:36.560
他们说我们的人马上就到
They say ours should be here shortly.

06:36.570 --> 06:37.900
你们要提高警惕
I want you guys on full alert

06:37.910 --> 06:40.020
时刻准备行动  好吗
And get all geared up, all right?

06:40.030 --> 06:41.070
他们在那
It's them!

06:41.080 --> 06:42.880
别动
Stop!

07:02.480 --> 07:04.890
他们会在任何一层楼出现
They could be on any floor.

07:04.900 --> 07:06.710
你能控制所有的门锁吗
Can you override the door locks?

07:06.720 --> 07:07.730
可以  都是电子锁
Yeah, they're electronic.

07:07.740 --> 07:08.930
我们在楼下控制
We control everything from down here.

07:08.940 --> 07:12.860
我要酒店的所有房间门都锁上
I want every room in this hotel locked down now!

07:16.750 --> 07:18.690
我们为什么不走楼梯去天台
Why don't we just take the stairs to the roof?

07:18.700 --> 07:20.740
因为我们将拉响火警
Because we'll set off the fire alarm.

07:20.750 --> 07:23.330
通过顶楼房间上方夹层的管道
The ducts in the crawl spaces above these top floor rooms,

07:23.340 --> 07:25.950
才是我们到天台的通道
That's how we get our rooftop access.

07:25.960 --> 07:27.780
只要我们找到了洗衣房的通风口
Once we find the laundry vent,

07:27.790 --> 07:30.230
我们就从那里到卸货区
We take that down to the loading dock.

07:37.720 --> 07:39.550
门全锁了
That should do it.

08:05.080 --> 08:06.800
出什么事了
What's going on?

08:07.630 --> 08:09.160
他们把我们关在门外了
They locked us out.

08:09.170 --> 08:10.410
我们到不了天台
We can't get to the roof.

08:10.420 --> 08:11.580
那我们往回走下楼去
Let's head back down.

08:11.590 --> 08:12.940
警察会在楼梯井等着我们
There'll be cops in the stairwell.

08:12.950 --> 08:15.610
无论上下  我们都走投无路了
We can't go up, we can't go down...

08:16.300 --> 08:18.060
我们被困住了
We're trapped.

08:23.600 --> 08:26.290
熊猫湾暗杀事件现在有了新的进展
There has been a new development in the Panda Bay assassination.

08:26.300 --> 08:27.890
有匿名消息透露
An anonymous source has provided Fox

08:27.900 --> 08:31.150
有文件显示  布鲁斯和斯科菲尔德
With documents showing a wire transfer

08:31.160 --> 08:34.020
从中国特工处得到了一笔汇款
From Chinese operatives to Burrows and Scofield.

08:34.030 --> 08:36.240
从地理政治角度来看
The fallout from this from a geopolitical standpoint

08:36.250 --> 08:38.160
这件事的负面影响震惊世人
Is staggering.

08:38.170 --> 08:40.130
中国和印度的关系...
Relations between China and India...

08:40.130 --> 08:41.440
南都联系我们了
Nandu reached out.

08:41.450 --> 08:44.580
他想见你
He wants to meet with you.

08:44.590 --> 08:46.310
这事只能这么办了
This couldn't have worked out better.

08:46.320 --> 08:48.450
中方的假文件伪造得不错
Nice audible on the Chinese document.

08:48.460 --> 08:50.700
谢谢
Thank you.

08:50.710 --> 08:53.490
现在  我们只要
Now we just...

08:53.500 --> 08:55.800
静观其变就可以了
Watch the dominoes begin to fall.

08:57.350 --> 09:00.130
我希望他们不要为难迈克尔
I just wish they weren't falling on Michael.

09:00.140 --> 09:03.000
克里斯蒂娜  你给过他活路
Christina, you gave him options,

09:03.010 --> 09:05.570
他走了自己的路  选择和我们干到底
He made his choice, he picked his side.

09:07.010 --> 09:09.640
是的  但他终究是我儿子
Yes, but he is my son.

09:13.700 --> 09:15.680
我唯一的儿子
My only son.

09:15.690 --> 09:17.110
现在  我们相信
And right now it is believed

09:17.120 --> 09:18.530
布鲁斯和斯科菲尔德
Both Burrows and Scofield

09:18.540 --> 09:19.810
仍然在酒店里
Are still in the hotel,

09:19.820 --> 09:22.320
警方正一步步缩小包围圈
But it appears the police are closing in.

09:22.330 --> 09:27.300
熊猫湾酒店  现场报道
Live just outside the Panda Bay Hotel...

09:27.710 --> 09:29.690
不行  迈克尔  这就是问题所在
No, no, no, you see, that's the problem, Michael.

09:29.700 --> 09:31.020
到处都是警察
There's cops everywhere.

09:31.030 --> 09:32.880
就好像是蚂蚁们倾巢出动了一样
It's like a freaking cop anthill out here.

09:32.890 --> 09:35.880
他们找到你们只不过是时间问题
Look, it's just a matter of time till they find you anyway.

09:35.890 --> 09:38.030
搞清楚他们的进攻方案
Find out what their plan of attack is.

09:38.040 --> 09:39.530
好啊  告诉你
Sure, you know what?

09:39.540 --> 09:41.890
我现在就过去问问他们  行了吧
Yeah, I'll just go up and ask them, all right?

09:41.900 --> 09:43.700
他们非常和蔼可亲
They look like a real friendly bunch.

09:43.710 --> 09:46.030
我们没多少时间了  速战速决吧
We don't have much time, so get it done now!

09:49.240 --> 09:51.400
布鲁斯和斯科菲尔德有可能全副武装
Burrows and Scofield could be armed to the teeth.

09:51.410 --> 09:52.710
楼梯的空间很窄
It's tight quarters in the stairwell,

09:52.720 --> 09:54.180
我不想看到枪战  明白吗
So I don't want a lot of shooting, all right?

09:54.190 --> 09:55.220
这家伙是国土安全局的
This guy's from Homeland Security.

09:55.230 --> 09:56.880
我逮捕了枪手之后
I'll file my report as soon as

09:56.890 --> 09:58.220
就会把报告发过去
I've apprehended the shooters.

09:58.230 --> 10:00.940
队长  我希望你搞明白
Whoa, whoa, let me be clear here, captain.

10:00.950 --> 10:02.060
今天的暗杀
The shooting that happened today

10:02.070 --> 10:03.440
不是普通的团伙暴力
Wasn't your typical gangbanger,

10:03.450 --> 10:05.610
迈阿密的破案环境是不是让你退化了
Public service killing you're used to here in Miami.

10:05.620 --> 10:08.700
这是国际性质的暗杀活动
This was an international assassination with ramifications

10:08.710 --> 10:10.910
直接影响了我们国家的安全
That directly affect the security of this country.

10:10.920 --> 10:12.950
如果  你再对我爱理不理的
So, if you turn your back on me again,

10:12.960 --> 10:15.860
我会以妨碍联邦调查让你吃不了兜着走
I'll jam you up for hindering a federal investigation.

10:15.860 --> 10:16.760
你明白吗
You understand?

10:18.770 --> 10:20.240
好吧
Fine.

10:20.250 --> 10:21.910
但是  你要跟在我后面
But I want you on my hip.

10:21.920 --> 10:24.210
我不会让你来转一圈之后
I'm not gonna have you running around playing

10:24.220 --> 10:25.880
让你回去好跟你的朋友吹嘘
So you can go back to your buddies at the office

10:25.890 --> 10:27.800
你经历过真正的枪林弹雨  懂吗
And tell them you saw some real gun play, understood?

10:27.810 --> 10:29.020
没问题
Not a problem.

10:29.030 --> 10:30.220
那你现在告诉我
Now, why don't you start by telling me

