Don't make a move for that weapon, Burrows.

24:45.740 --> 24:46.740
把面罩摘了
Take the masks off.

24:46.740 --> 24:48.980
立刻摘了
Take them off now!

24:52.600 --> 24:54.550
手放到脑后
Hands behind your head.

24:54.550 --> 24:56.340
你们最好祈祷
You'd better pray to god that

24:56.340 --> 24:58.300
我的手下没有出事
My men are found out all right.

24:58.300 --> 24:59.750
不过是个冲击波
It was a concussive blast.

24:59.750 --> 25:01.100
他们只是失去知觉了
They're just unconscious.

25:01.110 --> 25:03.020
闭嘴
Shut up.

25:04.560 --> 25:06.110
放松
Easy!

25:06.110 --> 25:08.110
放松
Easy.

25:08.110 --> 25:11.110
就像他刚说的那样  别想动手拿枪
And I'd follow that advice about not going for your guns.

25:11.120 --> 25:16.090
将军要你们回他办公室一趟
The general would like you back at the office.

25:17.620 --> 25:19.240
就现在
Now.

25:37.420 --> 25:40.900
酒店的事进展顺利吗
Did all go well at the hotel?

25:40.900 --> 25:44.620
我妈妈和莎拉怎么样
What's going on with Sara and my mother?

25:44.620 --> 25:46.210
克里斯蒂娜逃走了
Christina escaped.

25:46.210 --> 25:47.570
莎拉没事
Sara's okay.

25:47.580 --> 25:49.210
她还在公寓里
She's in the condo.

25:49.210 --> 25:53.100
打扰一下  你俩是不是想单独聚一聚
Excuse me, would you boys like a little alone time to catch up?

25:53.100 --> 25:55.050
你究竟想要我们做什么
What exactly do you expect from us?

25:55.050 --> 25:57.270
你们得为自己的过失负责
You need to take responsibility for your failures.

25:57.270 --> 25:59.050
我们没有失手
Hey, we failed nothing.

25:59.050 --> 26:01.250
整件事都是个圈套
This whole thing was a setup.

26:01.260 --> 26:04.890
-你明知道  -林肯·布鲁斯果然聪明
- You know it.  - Lincoln Burrows was outsmarted.

26:04.890 --> 26:06.560
谁能料想到那是陷阱呢
Who could have anticipated that?

26:12.600 --> 26:15.070
你得面对现实  一切都已经结束了
I think you need to accept that this is over.

26:17.940 --> 26:21.960
我手上的筹码握得太久了
I've been holding a chip for far too long.

26:21.960 --> 26:25.180
是时候出手了
It's time to play it.

26:25.910 --> 26:28.630
我们有过君子协议
I made you boys a promise.

26:28.630 --> 26:30.300
你们找回锡拉
You would find Scylla

26:30.300 --> 26:34.450
我给你们一笔钱
And I would see to it you got some cash

26:34.460 --> 26:35.810
并毁掉那份名单
And had the slate wiped clean.

26:35.810 --> 26:38.640
我仍想遵守协议
I intend to keep that promise.

26:38.640 --> 26:41.600
然而  如果遵守了一项协议
However, if I keep one promise,

26:41.600 --> 26:43.730
所有的协议都得遵守
I have to keep them all.

26:44.150 --> 26:45.800
现在
Now...

26:45.800 --> 26:47.650
我想看看
I wonder

26:47.650 --> 26:50.820
谁才是那个大赢家
Who the big winner will be.

26:50.820 --> 26:53.940
-别这么做  -别做什么
- Don't do this.  - Don't do what?

26:53.940 --> 26:55.650
我寄信给你们的时候
When I sent you those envelopes,

26:55.650 --> 26:57.190
并不是跟你们开玩笑
I wasn't just playing games

26:57.200 --> 26:59.200
我说得很清楚
I made it very clear

26:59.200 --> 27:00.600
你们只有一天时间
That you had one day

27:00.600 --> 27:02.780
来完成任务
To accomplish your job,

27:02.780 --> 27:05.670
否则后果自负
Or there would be consequences.

27:05.670 --> 27:06.990
那是什么
What's that?

27:06.990 --> 27:08.540
后果
The consequence.

27:08.540 --> 27:10.260
打电话给我们王后区的手下
Call our man in Queens.

27:11.380 --> 27:13.160
王后区  你打电话到纽约干什么
Queens? What are you calling New York for?

27:13.160 --> 27:14.930
麻烦打开免提
Put it on speaker, please.

27:16.380 --> 27:19.380
-请讲  -对4号目标采取行动
- Yes. - Move on Subject Four.

27:19.380 --> 27:20.550
我就一条街的距离
I'm a block away.

27:20.550 --> 27:22.840
预计两分钟内到达
ETA is less than two minutes.

27:22.840 --> 27:24.150
你个王八蛋
You son of a bitch.

27:24.720 --> 27:26.060
你个王八蛋
You son of a bitch!

27:26.060 --> 27:28.010
我老婆只是个手无缚鸡之力的女人
My wife is a defenseless woman.

27:28.010 --> 27:31.150
赛尔夫先生没有透露过他有个老婆  是吧
Mr. Self didn't inform you that he had a wife, did he?

27:31.150 --> 27:33.550
换了是我  也不会说的
Well, I wouldn't talk about my wife either

27:33.550 --> 27:35.900
要是我有点喝高了  酒后驾车
if I'd had a few too many Bourbons, got behind the wheel,

27:35.900 --> 27:40.520
不小心就把个绝代佳人碾成了花椰菜
And turned a beautiful young woman into a piece of broccoli.

27:40.520 --> 27:41.540
别伤害她
Don't do anything.

27:41.540 --> 27:45.080
我猜那才是你要携带锡拉潜逃的原因
I assume that is why you tried to run away with Scylla?

27:45.080 --> 27:47.490
辜负了一个福利只够支付你
To screw a government that was giving you benefits

27:47.490 --> 27:51.430
一个小县城环城高速监管费的政府
that would only pay for a county facility overlooking the belt parkway,

27:51.430 --> 27:55.720
你转手卖了锡拉  你和她就可以从此消失
and to sell it so that you and she could disappear

27:55.720 --> 27:58.310
改头换面  永远逍遥快活了
And be hidden forever.

27:59.710 --> 28:01.010
这就是生活[法语]
C'est la vie.

28:01.010 --> 28:02.180
我看到目标了
I have the subject in sights.

28:02.180 --> 28:05.370
她在医院的院子里坐在轮椅上
She's in a wheelchair under a tree in the hospital courtyard.

28:05.370 --> 28:06.160
可以动手了吗
Do I have a go?

28:06.160 --> 28:07.180
求求你别伤害她
Please don't do this.

28:07.180 --> 28:10.180
求你了  你们可以杀我  你们杀我吧
Okay, please, you can kill me, okay, you can kill me

28:10.190 --> 28:11.940
现在就行  求你了  杀我吧
Right now, please, kill me.

28:11.940 --> 28:14.070
你没必要这样  我们会拿到锡拉的
You don't need to do this. We'll get Scylla.

28:14.070 --> 28:15.270
那才是我想听的答案
That's what I wanted to hear.

28:15.270 --> 28:16.390
那是我们正在做的
Well that's what we'r trying to do

28:16.390 --> 28:18.280
-我们快找到了  -但你们必须知道
- We're getting it. - But you have to know what awaits you

28:18.280 --> 28:21.780
如果失败  等待你们和自己爱人的下场
And your loved ones if you don't.

28:21.780 --> 28:23.060
我们都明白
We understand, okay?

28:23.060 --> 28:24.580
-执行命令  -求求你别这样
- Execute the order. - Please don't do it!

28:25.950 --> 28:28.090
天哪
Oh, my god, oh, my god!

28:28.090 --> 28:30.640
救命  救命
Get help, hel--!

28:34.960 --> 28:38.510
我想你刚才请求了死刑
I believe you made a request.

29:06.740 --> 29:09.410
蒂博格  确保他死定了
Bagwell, make sure he's dead.

29:09.410 --> 29:13.210
大家现在都明白了吗
Does everyone understand now?

29:15.800 --> 29:19.420
我们现在可以同心协力了吗
Are we all on the same page?

29:21.010 --> 29:23.120
很好
Good.

29:23.120 --> 29:25.760
开工了  开工了
Let's get down to business.

29:26.680 --> 29:29.630
7.5亿美元
Three-quarters of a billion dollars

29:29.630 --> 29:32.470
在卢森堡  用的是匿名账户
In a numerical account in Luxembourg.

29:32.470 --> 29:35.690
如果你还关心慈善工作的话
If you are still worried about humanitarian efforts,

29:35.690 --> 29:38.710
给联合国儿童基金会写张支票
Write a check to UNICEF.

29:40.190 --> 29:43.830
24小时内所有数据就会送到
All the data will be delivered within 24 hours.

29:43.830 --> 29:46.880
正合我意
That's what I expected.

29:52.420 --> 29:54.700
你的计划非常成功
You played it perfectly.

29:58.330 --> 30:01.300
联系下我们在中国的联系人
Reach out to our contact in China.

30:01.300 --> 30:05.070
我感觉他们可能也会对我们的货很感兴趣
I have a feeling they may be interested in what we're selling as well.

30:09.000 --> 30:11.000
克里斯蒂娜  我不建议
Christina, I don't advise

30:11.010 --> 30:12.640
脚踩两只船
Playing both sides of this coin.

30:12.640 --> 30:14.140
瘦猪有食吃
Pigs get fat

30:14.140 --> 30:16.310
肥猪一刀死
And hogs get slaughtered.

30:22.230 --> 30:26.500
去联系中国的联系人
Reach out to China.

30:38.530 --> 30:40.000
不  让我们的人
No! Keep our people

30:40.000 --> 30:42.890
守好佛罗里达和乔治亚州的每个私人机场
At every private airfield in Florida and in Georgia.

30:42.890 --> 30:45.090
我们不能让克里斯蒂娜离开这个州
We can't have Christina leaving the state.

30:45.090 --> 30:47.930
她在玩弄印度人的感情
She played on India's emotions,

30:47.930 --> 30:49.230
可能说明她想在今天与
Which probably means she'd want to meet

30:49.230 --> 30:50.880
其中一个大使会面
With one of their emissaries today

30:50.880 --> 30:51.900
趁自己还很受欢迎
While they're still running hot.

30:51.900 --> 30:53.380
她可能还在迈阿密
She could still be in Miami,

30:53.380 --> 30:54.430
或许就在大使馆里
Maybe at the embassy.

30:54.430 --> 30:57.050
不  她不会在大使馆的
No. She's not at the embassy.

30:57.050 --> 30:58.390
她和印度做的任何交易
Any deal she makes with India

30:58.390 --> 30:59.600
都会绝对地保密
Will be strictly off the radar.

30:59.600 --> 31:02.360
现在她关心的只有2件事
Right now she's concerned with two things.

31:02.360 --> 31:04.360
一件是将锡拉卖出去
One is closing the deal on Scylla,

31:04.360 --> 31:06.390
我先假定她已经完成了
Which I'm assuming she's already done,

31:06.390 --> 31:08.160
第二件事就是拿到钱
And the second is getting paid.

31:08.910 --> 31:10.710
没有赛尔夫的踪迹
No sign of Self.

31:12.230 --> 31:13.730
卖掉锡拉她能拿到多少钱
How much can she get for Scylla?

31:13.730 --> 31:16.740
印度的5亿美金  还有中国的5亿
Half a billion from India, the same from China.

31:16.740 --> 31:17.750
海外账户
Overseas account?

31:17.760 --> 31:19.070
国外电汇吗
Foreign wire transfer?

31:19.070 --> 31:22.290
我怀疑她不会收普通支票
I doubt she's taking any food stamps.

31:22.290 --> 31:24.260
她会确认
She's going to want confirmation

31:24.260 --> 31:25.800
在她离开美国之前
That that money is safely overseas

31:25.800 --> 31:28.380
那些钱在海外账户是安全的
Before she leaves the U.S.

31:28.380 --> 31:30.420
我们找到那些钱
We find the money,

31:30.420 --> 31:31.600
我们就找到了我母亲
We find my mother.

31:31.600 --> 31:34.300
通常国际电汇的结算
Normally it takes three business days

31:34.310 --> 31:35.970
需要三个工作日
For an international wire transfer to clear,

31:35.970 --> 31:40.890
除非是一家美联储授权的银行
Unless the bank is a Federal Reserve Signatory, in which case

31:40.900 --> 31:42.310
那样的话转账会立即生效
The transfer is immediate.

31:42.310 --> 31:43.900
你觉得她会亲自去银行吗
You think she'll head to the bank?

31:43.900 --> 31:46.230
她只要从买家已经从海外转账过来的
All she has to do is withdraw a few grand from the millions

31:46.230 --> 31:50.420
上百万美元里面取出几千块
That that buyer has probably transferred overseas already.

31:50.570 --> 31:52.240
她就知道了钱全到账了
She'll know it's all there.

31:52.240 --> 31:55.160
那么只要我们找到一家美联储授权的
So let's find a Federal Reserve Signatory bank in Miami.

31:55.160 --> 31:56.610
迈阿密银行  我们就有机会找到她
We'll have a shot at finding her.

31:56.610 --> 31:58.380
还有锡拉
And Scylla.

31:58.380 --> 31:59.880
你瞧  迈克尔  这就是
There, Michael, you see, that's

31:59.880 --> 32:03.280
为什么我刚才没有把你的名字放在碗里
Why I didn't put your name in the bowl.

32:03.280 --> 32:05.140
你是这里唯一无法取代的人
You're the only one here that's irreplaceable.

32:05.140 --> 32:06.850
探员  线人  打手
Agents, informants, muscle--

32:06.850 --> 32:08.620
他们都可胜任  但是...
They're nice to have, but...

32:08.620 --> 32:09.810
他们都是可以取代的
Finally they're replaceable.

32:09.810 --> 32:12.590
附近有家支行  大概20分钟的路程
There's a branch about 20 minutes away.

32:12.590 --> 32:14.230
你的头脑
That mind of yours--

32:14.230 --> 32:16.430
简直是百万里挑一的
It's one in a million.

32:16.430 --> 32:18.630
很高兴看到它终于为我所用了
Nice to see it finally working for me.

32:18.630 --> 32:20.600
我不是为你干的
I do not work for you.

32:20.600 --> 32:22.940
走着瞧
Not yet.

32:39.010 --> 32:40.340
是合法的
It's legitimate,

32:40.350 --> 32:42.350
我向你保证
I assure you.

32:42.350 --> 32:44.430
好的
Oh, okay.

32:44.430 --> 32:46.830
我想取回10000美元现金
I just want to withdraw the $10,000

32:46.830 --> 32:50.720
以确定卢森堡账户是否已准确无误地建好
So I can be sure the Luxembourg account is properly set up.

32:50.720 --> 32:52.470
当然
Of course.

33:10.990 --> 33:12.410
她在里面吗
Is she in there?

33:12.410 --> 33:14.080
是  我从窗子那看见她
Yeah, I saw her through the window.

33:14.080 --> 33:16.380
正和一个高个的黑发男子说话
She's talking to a tall, dark-haired guy.

33:16.380 --> 33:18.700
他们就是在酒店里面陷害我们的人
They're the same guys who set us up at the hotel.

33:18.700 --> 33:20.310
我们等她出来  杀他们个措手不及
We wait until she comes out, just jump them.

33:20.310 --> 33:23.300
那么  我们怎么对付她的保镖呢
So... What do we do about her security?

33:23.300 --> 33:26.010
要想对付她  得先搞定她的保镖
I mean, we jump her, we gotta jump the guys she's with,

33:26.010 --> 33:27.740
天知道  还会有多少探员会像蚂蚁一样
And God knows how many other agents are gonna come crawling

33:27.740 --> 33:29.700
从门外冲进来
Out of the woodwork like ants.

33:32.680 --> 33:36.270
听着  我不想说得这么直白
Look, um... I hate to bring up the obvious,

33:36.270 --> 33:39.100
但是我记得上次  你们俩依然对
But last time I checked, you two still disagreed

33:39.100 --> 33:43.370
锡拉到手后如何处置  各有打算
As to what to do with Scylla If we actually get it.

33:45.190 --> 33:47.030
是啊  我猜就是这样
Yeah, that's what I thought.

33:47.030 --> 33:48.360
别说这烂事了
Well, let's skip the damn thing.

33:48.360 --> 33:49.580
我是说  谁能拦住我们
I mean, who's gonna stop us?

33:49.580 --> 33:50.810
就凭一个17岁的小保安弟弟吗
A 17-year-old security guard?

33:50.810 --> 33:52.830
不是  可能是那个拿枪的家伙
No, probably the guy with the gun.

33:52.830 --> 33:56.140
他一看到我们的脸就会开火
He'll open fire as soon as he sees our faces.

33:57.260 --> 34:01.810
那么  或许可以不让他们看到我们的脸
Then, uh... maybe they shouldn't see our faces.

34:03.500 --> 34:05.460
然后送披萨的来了
So then the pizza guy showed up,

34:05.460 --> 34:07.130
然后韦恩从树丛里跳出来
And Wayne jumped out of the bushes

34:07.130 --> 34:08.880
想要把披萨抢过去  但是...
And tried to grab the pizza, but the...

34:08.880 --> 34:10.800
但是那个家伙...
But the guy...

34:10.800 --> 34:13.190
我的天啊
My god.

34:19.060 --> 34:20.730
你还好吗  先生
Are you okay, Mister?

34:22.110 --> 34:23.310
没事
Yeah.

34:23.310 --> 34:24.450
去打911
Go call 911.

34:24.450 --> 34:25.870
-快去  -别去
- Go, go. - No.

34:25.870 --> 34:27.900
别去  别打给任何人
No, don't call anyone.

34:27.900 --> 34:29.900
行吗
Okay?

34:29.900 --> 34:31.820
别打给任何人
Don't call anybody.

34:31.820 --> 34:34.740
别打给任何人
Don't call anyone.

34:37.830 --> 34:41.620
你知道吗  一旦那个弟弟拿到了
You know, once baby brother's got his little hands

34:41.620 --> 34:42.950
你的"魔法盒子"
On that magic box of yours,

34:42.950 --> 34:44.620
他要是想骗过马吉拉大猩猩[指代将军]
I don't think it's going to be too hard for him

34:44.620 --> 34:45.870
简直就是易如反掌
To trick Magilla Gorilla,

34:45.870 --> 34:47.170
你知道我是什么意思吧
If you know what I'm saying.

34:47.170 --> 34:49.260
不  我不知道
No, I don't.

34:49.260 --> 34:50.590
你还真以为
And you really think

34:50.590 --> 34:52.010
斯科菲尔德会不顾他侄子的安危
That Scofield's going to risk his nephew's life?

34:52.010 --> 34:54.010
他把"头等奖"交给"坏人"之前
He's gonna figure out something

34:54.010 --> 34:56.400
肯定会想出点别的坏点子来的
Before he hands first prize over to the bad guys.

34:56.400 --> 34:59.070
斯科菲尔德想得很单纯  就像童子军
Scofield thinks pure, like a little cub scout.

34:59.070 --> 35:02.050
布鲁斯  他的思维也很幼稚
Burrows, he just thinks like a cub.

35:02.050 --> 35:03.600
他说得对
He's right.

35:03.610 --> 35:05.270
斯科菲尔德在外面拿着我想要的东西
I don't feel comfortable having Scofield

35:05.270 --> 35:06.610
而我困在这却没有他的把柄
Out there with something I want

35:06.610 --> 35:08.940
我可不放心
While I'm stuck here with nothing he wants.

35:08.940 --> 35:10.610
我需要筹码
I need leverage.

35:10.610 --> 35:13.910
你看见他们刚过来的时候
You saw the way Mahone pulled Scofield over

35:13.920 --> 35:15.920
马宏把他拉到一边去了吧
When they first got here.

35:15.920 --> 35:17.250
我打赌他们说的肯定是关于
Bet you a wooden nickel they was talking

35:17.250 --> 35:20.670
女医生和她的藏身之处
About little Dr. Underpants and her whereabouts.

35:20.670 --> 35:22.840
但是我们不知道在什么地方
Too bad we don't know where that is.

35:22.840 --> 35:24.680
又错了  卷发小子
Wrong again, curly.

35:24.680 --> 35:27.180
你们都在这嚼口香糖的时候
While everyone was up here flapping their gums,

35:27.180 --> 35:29.550
